00:40:35.359 --> 00:40:37.670
hold of it.

00:40:40.240 --> 00:40:43.990
I liked what I heard about

00:40:44.000 --> 00:40:46.790
John Bevere's book today from what

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:50.950
my wife read me.

00:40:50.960 --> 00:40:53.589
I hope that

00:40:53.599 --> 00:40:55.589
blessed you. I tried

00:40:55.599 --> 00:40:57.190
not to make it too long, but I ended up

00:40:57.200 --> 00:40:59.349
talking too much.

00:41:02.000 --> 00:41:05.109
Then I saw

00:41:05.119 --> 00:41:09.510
this man be assassinated

00:41:09.520 --> 00:41:11.829
on a stage with microphones in front of

00:41:11.839 --> 00:41:14.470
him. He was behind a pulpit

00:41:14.480 --> 00:41:16.870
talking to a crowd,

00:41:16.880 --> 00:41:20.390
and it looked like he was appointed

00:41:20.400 --> 00:41:23.750
to be the leader over that nation.

00:41:23.760 --> 00:41:27.670
As he was talking,

00:41:27.670 --> 00:41:27.680
someone

00:41:27.680 --> 00:41:30.069
from the right

00:41:30.079 --> 00:41:33.190
took

00:41:33.200 --> 00:41:35.510
him out.

00:41:35.510 --> 00:41:35.520
It

00:41:35.520 --> 00:41:37.750
went through his

00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:40.150
collarbone

00:41:40.150 --> 00:41:40.160
area—he

00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:41.910
probably had a bulletproof vest

00:41:41.910 --> 00:41:41.920
on—but

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:43.829
it went

00:41:43.839 --> 00:41:46.630
through his neck area and

00:41:46.640 --> 00:41:51.430
out.

00:41:51.440 --> 00:41:54.870
He was done.

00:41:54.880 --> 00:41:56.630
As I watched this, I heard the people

00:41:56.640 --> 00:41:58.550
screaming. I could see it in the vision.

00:41:58.560 --> 00:42:00.150
I heard the people screaming

00:42:00.150 --> 00:42:00.160
and

00:42:00.160 --> 00:42:02.630
acting up, freaking out

00:42:02.640 --> 00:42:05.109
because of what they just witnessed. But

00:42:05.119 --> 00:42:07.190
they brought in

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:10.390
another after this man was taken over. I

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:12.630
saw this man

00:42:12.640 --> 00:42:16.230
after he was done; I saw a bad leader

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:19.270
come in again, and the

00:42:19.270 --> 00:42:19.280
Lord—I

00:42:19.280 --> 00:42:22.470
heard Him say, "I told you the window of

00:42:22.470 --> 00:42:22.480
this."I

00:42:22.480 --> 00:42:24.790
mean, I told you this would be

00:42:24.800 --> 00:42:27.030
a window,

00:42:27.040 --> 00:42:29.030
not a

00:42:29.030 --> 00:42:29.040
door—not

00:42:29.040 --> 00:42:33.270
like Cuba, not like Mexico, not like

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:35.829
Venezuela. I'll bring in leaders for

00:42:35.839 --> 00:42:37.510
those nations, and great revival will come

00:42:37.520 --> 00:42:39.910
forth out of there, but there'll be a

00:42:39.920 --> 00:42:44.069
longer time frame. I saw Iran flip

00:42:44.079 --> 00:42:48.390
quickly back to bringing in some bozo

00:42:48.400 --> 00:42:52.950
like the Ayatollah again.

00:42:52.960 --> 00:42:55.910
It was a window for the church to have a

00:42:55.920 --> 00:43:01.030
major revival.

00:43:01.040 --> 00:43:06.150
So I pray for that man, Reza Pahlavi, or

00:43:06.160 --> 00:43:09.510
whatever his name is.

00:43:09.520 --> 00:43:12.069
I pray for his safety. I don't wish

00:43:12.079 --> 00:43:13.829
evil upon anybody; I tell you what I

00:43:13.839 --> 00:43:16.550
see. It was

00:43:16.550 --> 00:43:16.560
a

00:43:16.560 --> 00:43:19.910
very colorful vision,

00:43:19.920 --> 00:43:23.510
very bold. I

00:43:23.520 --> 00:43:25.109
could see the microphones that were in

00:43:25.119 --> 00:43:27.589
front of his face.

00:43:27.599 --> 00:43:30.390
I don't know where he was.

00:43:30.400 --> 00:43:33.750
It looked to be like sandstone buildings

00:43:33.760 --> 00:43:37.670
around him. They were like a yellow-looking color, almost

00:43:37.670 --> 00:43:37.680
like a burnt red-orange

00:43:37.680 --> 00:43:40.790
looking color

00:43:40.800 --> 00:43:44.390
building—some

00:43:44.400 --> 00:43:46.150
kind of

00:43:46.160 --> 00:43:48.630
sandstone

00:43:48.630 --> 00:43:48.640
or

00:43:48.640 --> 00:43:51.589
stucco.

00:43:51.599 --> 00:43:57.510
But as I saw that,

00:43:57.520 --> 00:44:01.910
it was short-lived.

00:44:01.920 --> 00:44:03.910
You can let a bird out of a cage,

00:44:03.920 --> 00:44:05.910
but if they know how to live in

00:44:05.920 --> 00:44:08.790
bondage and they've never been free before,

00:44:08.800 --> 00:44:11.589
they don't know how to fly.

00:44:11.599 --> 00:44:13.030
They don't know how to get out and be

00:44:13.040 --> 00:44:15.829
done. They're so used to living in

00:44:15.839 --> 00:44:17.750
bondage. People have been so used to living in

00:44:17.760 --> 00:44:19.750
bondage for decade after decade

00:44:19.760 --> 00:44:24.069
since the 1970s. They said when the

00:44:24.069 --> 00:44:24.079
Ayatollah got

00:44:24.079 --> 00:44:25.750
in there, and then here we

00:44:25.760 --> 00:44:28.710
are. You can free them, but are they

00:44:28.720 --> 00:44:31.349
free inside? It’s

00:44:31.349 --> 00:44:31.359
the

00:44:31.359 --> 00:44:33.990
same thing with Egypt, the same thing with

00:44:34.000 --> 00:44:36.390
the children

00:44:36.400 --> 00:44:39.030
of Israel coming out of Egypt. They were

00:44:39.040 --> 00:44:42.069
bound inside their minds, and it took a

00:44:42.079 --> 00:44:44.630
whole new generation to come up and let the

00:44:44.640 --> 00:44:46.870
old ones die off before they could go

00:44:46.880 --> 00:44:49.670
and take the land. You've got to get

00:44:49.680 --> 00:44:51.990
stinking thinking out of your thinking

00:44:52.000 --> 00:44:53.829
and realize that you're more than a

00:44:53.829 --> 00:44:53.839
conqueror—that

00:44:53.839 --> 00:44:56.150
God has come to set you

00:44:56.160 --> 00:44:58.390
free.

00:44:58.400 --> 00:45:00.470
But as long as you think bound, you'll

00:45:00.480 --> 00:45:03.030
be bound. As a man thinketh in his

00:45:03.040 --> 00:45:05.829
heart, so is he. And that's what the

00:45:05.839 --> 00:45:07.750
Lord is showing me. I can free them,

00:45:07.760 --> 00:45:10.470
Brandon. I can free them, but they're

00:45:10.480 --> 00:45:12.630
not free. Even if I let them out

00:45:12.630 --> 00:45:12.640
and

00:45:12.640 --> 00:45:15.910
open the cage door and say, "Free bird,

00:45:15.910 --> 00:45:15.920
fly,"they're

00:45:15.920 --> 00:45:18.790
so used to being on that

00:45:18.800 --> 00:45:20.550
perch,

00:45:20.560 --> 00:45:22.390
being the one

00:45:22.400 --> 00:45:24.870
trapped, that they don't realize the

00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:27.270
door's open and they have an opportunity.

00:45:27.280 --> 00:45:29.109
They still think back and go back

00:45:29.119 --> 00:45:31.589
to the way they were in bondage. It was

00:45:31.599 --> 00:45:34.150
better in Egypt.

00:45:34.160 --> 00:45:38.390
It was better in Egypt.

00:45:38.400 --> 00:45:40.069
Even after I freed them: "It's better in

00:45:40.069 --> 00:45:40.079
Egypt."I

00:45:40.079 --> 00:45:42.950
give them manna from

00:45:42.950 --> 00:45:42.960
heaven—and

00:45:42.960 --> 00:45:44.950
John said in that book,

00:45:44.960 --> 00:45:47.589
it was boxcars full of

00:45:47.589 --> 00:45:47.599
manna.

00:45:47.599 --> 00:45:49.829
Every morning God provided a

00:45:49.839 --> 00:45:51.349
miracle—huge

00:45:51.359 --> 00:45:54.150
amounts of food, thousands and

00:45:54.160 --> 00:45:55.990
thousands of pounds for millions of

00:45:56.000 --> 00:45:57.829
people.

00:45:57.839 --> 00:46:00.550
Every morning God provided, but it's

00:46:00.560 --> 00:46:03.589
better in Egypt because Egypt was still

00:46:03.599 --> 00:46:07.430
inside of them.

00:46:07.440 --> 00:46:09.670
They didn't realize, "We're free. We can

00:46:09.680 --> 00:46:12.550
take the land. The God of Abraham,

00:46:12.560 --> 00:46:15.270
Isaac, and Jacob is with us."They didn't

00:46:15.280 --> 00:46:16.630
want to go up on the mountain; they sent

00:46:16.640 --> 00:46:22.069
Moses.

00:46:22.079 --> 00:46:24.870
I refuse to allow the devil to

00:46:24.880 --> 00:46:28.790
keep me bound in my thinking.

00:46:28.800 --> 00:46:31.349
It's time to come up higher and realize

00:46:31.359 --> 00:46:34.870
who we are.

00:46:34.880 --> 00:46:36.870
He's the accuser of the

00:46:36.880 --> 00:46:38.069
brethren, folks. He tries to tell

00:46:38.079 --> 00:46:39.990
you all the time you're a loser, but

00:46:40.000 --> 00:46:42.790
we're

00:46:42.790 --> 00:46:42.800
winners.

00:46:42.800 --> 00:46:45.349
Jesus made us winners;

00:46:45.359 --> 00:46:49.750
we're more than conquerors.

00:46:49.760 --> 00:46:51.270
So, Father, we just thank You

00:46:51.280 --> 00:46:54.870
for the body that was broken for us.

00:46:54.880 --> 00:46:58.630
As we praise You tonight for all

00:46:58.640 --> 00:47:01.109
that You've done for setting us free,

00:47:01.119 --> 00:47:03.990
Father, thank You, Lord, for the Iranian

00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:06.790
people, that they'll take hold of this

00:47:06.800 --> 00:47:08.550
opportunity

00:47:08.560 --> 00:47:11.829
and get ready for the greatest

00:47:11.839 --> 00:47:14.870
revival they've ever seen. It will be

00:47:14.880 --> 00:47:16.550
all around them if they'll grab hold

00:47:16.560 --> 00:47:19.589
of it—the church.

00:47:19.599 --> 00:47:22.790
They'll take this opportunity

00:47:22.800 --> 00:47:27.190
and bring in the souls

00:47:27.200 --> 00:47:30.950
all throughout the region.

00:47:30.960 --> 00:47:32.470
I thank You, Father, for the body that

00:47:32.480 --> 00:47:35.270
was broken. You were wounded for our

00:47:35.270 --> 00:47:35.280
transgressions;

00:47:35.280 --> 00:47:36.710
You were bruised for our

00:47:36.720 --> 00:47:38.309
iniquities. The chastisement of our

00:47:38.319 --> 00:47:40.069
peace was upon You, and with Your

00:47:40.079 --> 00:47:43.030
stripes, we are healed. We thank You,

00:47:43.040 --> 00:47:44.550
Lord, that we don't have to be sick in

00:47:44.560 --> 00:47:46.390
our bodies anymore.

00:47:46.400 --> 00:47:47.990
We thank You, Lord, that we walk in

00:47:48.000 --> 00:47:50.470
divine health, and we take this body in

00:47:50.480 --> 00:47:53.270
the name of Jesus and receive it by

00:47:53.280 --> 00:47:54.950
faith.

00:47:54.960 --> 00:47:56.950
We have a covenant.

00:47:56.960 --> 00:47:59.270
This is a cup of the covenant. Jesus

00:47:59.280 --> 00:48:01.829
took it all, and we don't have to have

00:48:01.839 --> 00:48:04.230
it. Father, I thank You, Lord, that our

00:48:04.240 --> 00:48:06.950
sins are forgiven. The moment we confess

00:48:06.960 --> 00:48:09.510
our sins, You are faithful and just to

00:48:09.520 --> 00:48:11.349
forgive us and cleanse us of

00:48:11.359 --> 00:48:13.990
all unrighteousness. We plead the

00:48:14.000 --> 00:48:16.230
blood, we apply the blood, and we make much

00:48:16.240 --> 00:48:17.829
of the blood. The blood makes much

00:48:17.839 --> 00:48:19.990
of us. We thank You, Lord. There's a

00:48:20.000 --> 00:48:22.309
bloodline around us: over my mind, over

00:48:22.319 --> 00:48:26.549
my health, over my finances,

00:48:26.559 --> 00:48:28.309
over my wife, my children, all of

00:48:28.309 --> 00:48:28.319
us—God,

00:48:28.319 --> 00:48:30.390
my dogs. Father, I thank You, Lord.

00:48:30.400 --> 00:48:33.030
The blessing of the Lord is on our

00:48:33.040 --> 00:48:35.670
house. Father, this is the beginning of

00:48:35.680 --> 00:48:37.910
March, and I thank You, Lord,

00:48:37.920 --> 00:48:39.670
that the blood moon was last night. The

00:48:39.680 --> 00:48:41.510
signs of the times are all around us

00:48:41.520 --> 00:48:44.470
again.

00:48:44.480 --> 00:48:47.829
You're screaming in the sky, Lord.

00:48:47.839 --> 00:48:49.349
You're yelling,

00:48:49.359 --> 00:48:51.510
telling everybody,

00:48:51.520 --> 00:48:55.190
"Are we listening?

00:48:55.200 --> 00:49:02.790
Are we listening to what You're

00:49:02.790 --> 00:49:02.800
saying?"I

00:49:02.800 --> 00:49:04.790
take this blood right now in the name

00:49:04.800 --> 00:49:08.150
of Jesus, and we apply it to us. Amen

00:49:08.160 --> 00:49:11.349
and amen.

00:49:11.359 --> 00:49:14.230
I have to say one more thing.

00:49:14.240 --> 00:49:17.030
I noticed

00:49:19.520 --> 00:49:21.589
about two or

00:49:21.599 --> 00:49:24.069
three weeks ago,

00:49:26.559 --> 00:49:29.589
when I hear Him and that cloak

00:49:29.599 --> 00:49:31.750
comes on, I feel like

00:49:31.760 --> 00:49:34.150
I can hear Him like

00:49:34.160 --> 00:49:36.790
I'm talking to Braden.

00:49:36.800 --> 00:49:38.950
It's that loud.

00:49:38.960 --> 00:49:41.349
But I noticed as I had gotten

00:49:41.349 --> 00:49:41.359
an

00:49:41.359 --> 00:49:42.870
offense in my heart—and

00:49:42.870 --> 00:49:42.880
we were

00:49:42.880 --> 00:49:44.309
reading "The Bait of

00:49:44.309 --> 00:49:44.319
Satan"and

00:49:44.319 --> 00:49:48.710
getting that offense

00:49:48.710 --> 00:49:48.720
out—it

00:49:48.720 --> 00:49:50.790
sounded like He was talking like

00:49:50.800 --> 00:49:52.630
this.

00:49:52.640 --> 00:49:55.589
I told

00:49:55.589 --> 00:49:55.599
Diana,

00:49:55.599 --> 00:50:00.069
"It's not deep; it's

00:50:00.069 --> 00:50:00.079
shallow."It's

00:50:00.079 --> 00:50:01.829
not like it's coming on all the

00:50:01.839 --> 00:50:04.069
way. I don't understand what's going on.

00:50:04.079 --> 00:50:05.990
But that's why I take time and I don't

00:50:06.000 --> 00:50:07.829
make videos; I get quiet. When I don't

00:50:07.839 --> 00:50:09.990
hear Him, I freeze.

00:50:10.000 --> 00:50:11.670
If you aren't hearing Him real clear, I

00:50:11.680 --> 00:50:15.349
check my thermostat.

00:50:15.359 --> 00:50:18.309
I know because He's always there and

00:50:18.319 --> 00:50:20.549
He's always talking to me, but when He

00:50:20.559 --> 00:50:22.150
talks

00:50:22.160 --> 00:50:23.589
and it doesn't sound very

00:50:23.589 --> 00:50:23.599
clear,

00:50:23.599 --> 00:50:25.670
like He's muffled,

00:50:25.680 --> 00:50:28.870
He's still saying the same thing.

00:50:28.880 --> 00:50:30.630
But as soon as that happens, I check

00:50:30.630 --> 00:50:30.640
my

00:50:30.640 --> 00:50:33.349
heart because it's the flesh

00:50:33.349 --> 00:50:33.359
that's

00:50:33.359 --> 00:50:37.030
in the way.

00:50:37.040 --> 00:50:39.349
So if you feel like God's

00:50:39.359 --> 00:50:40.630
trying to tell you

00:50:40.640 --> 00:50:42.230
something and you can't understand what

00:50:42.240 --> 00:50:43.829
He's saying, check your heart, check

00:50:43.839 --> 00:50:45.349
your flesh, check your thermostat.

00:50:45.359 --> 00:50:47.990
You're in the way.

00:50:48.000 --> 00:50:50.390
So I started saying, "Well, Lord,

00:50:50.400 --> 00:50:52.950
something's

00:50:52.950 --> 00:50:52.960
wrong."I

00:50:52.960 --> 00:50:55.510
took that time,

00:50:55.520 --> 00:50:57.589
and then Diana got sick

00:50:57.599 --> 00:51:00.150
with COVID and all that. I got real

00:51:00.160 --> 00:51:02.710
quiet, and

00:51:02.710 --> 00:51:02.720
He

00:51:02.720 --> 00:51:06.950
said, "Examine yourself.

00:51:06.960 --> 00:51:09.430
All it takes

00:51:09.440 --> 00:51:11.190
is to go

00:51:11.200 --> 00:51:13.510
just a little bit off course to go way

00:51:13.520 --> 00:51:16.230
off course over

00:51:16.230 --> 00:51:16.240
time."And

00:51:16.240 --> 00:51:17.510
that's what I was trying to tell you

00:51:17.520 --> 00:51:19.510
all as I was examining the offense in my

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:21.510
heart. The

00:51:21.520 --> 00:51:23.510
moment I started praying for those that

00:51:23.520 --> 00:51:25.910
despitefully used me and

00:51:25.910 --> 00:51:25.920
came

00:51:25.920 --> 00:51:27.349
against me—people I felt

00:51:27.359 --> 00:51:29.430
offended

00:51:29.430 --> 00:51:29.440
by—I

00:51:29.440 --> 00:51:31.349
started praying for them and

00:51:31.359 --> 00:51:33.589
lifting them up, and

00:51:38.160 --> 00:51:45.829
it became loud again.

00:51:45.839 --> 00:51:48.150
How do you love your brother?

00:51:48.160 --> 00:51:50.870
Check

00:51:50.880 --> 00:51:54.309
your love walk, your love thermostat.

00:51:54.319 --> 00:51:56.710
Love takes no account of a suffered

00:51:56.720 --> 00:51:58.549
wrong. What does that mean? I don't care

00:51:58.559 --> 00:51:59.910
who's talking trash about you; I'm

00:51:59.920 --> 00:52:02.470
walking in love. Check your love

00:52:02.480 --> 00:52:04.790
thermostat.

00:52:04.800 --> 00:52:07.430
I don't care what the email says or what

00:52:07.440 --> 00:52:09.109
you get in the mail from some sister

00:52:09.119 --> 00:52:10.710
that writes you a long letter telling

00:52:10.720 --> 00:52:13.670
you off. I don't care what you say,

00:52:13.680 --> 00:52:16.230
sister. I'm following what the voice of

00:52:16.240 --> 00:52:17.990
the Lord told me to do, and I forgive

00:52:18.000 --> 00:52:21.990
you. But it's easy to take offense.

00:52:22.000 --> 00:52:23.270
That's why I'm saying when you get that root

00:52:23.270 --> 00:52:23.280
of

00:52:23.280 --> 00:52:25.030
offense and you keep stacking them

00:52:25.040 --> 00:52:27.030
up in there,

00:52:27.040 --> 00:52:28.870
eventually he starts talking like

00:52:28.880 --> 00:52:31.589
this. But he's saying the same thing, and

00:52:31.599 --> 00:52:33.430
he's still there. What's wrong with you,

00:52:33.440 --> 00:52:37.030
Brandon? It's not my Father. Why are you

00:52:37.030 --> 00:52:37.040
talking

00:52:37.040 --> 00:52:39.670
like this, Lord?

00:52:39.680 --> 00:52:43.030
Why is it not so deep, Lord?

00:52:43.040 --> 00:52:44.870
Why doesn't it feel like that cloak

00:52:44.880 --> 00:52:46.549
coming on like it used to? What

00:52:46.559 --> 00:52:49.030
happened? I still feel it, but it's not

00:52:49.040 --> 00:52:51.430
like it was.

00:52:51.440 --> 00:52:53.910
What's wrong with me?

00:52:53.920 --> 00:52:55.349
The moment you start checking your

00:52:55.359 --> 00:52:57.910
